Testing color theory with @kanishhkkkaa using @simplynam.beauty Pixie Dust, and we’re officially obsessed! ✨ 

Its water-based, liquid-to-powder formula is lightweight, cooling, and completely non-sticky—an absolute dream to wear! 🌟 And for just ₹899, it’s a steal. Trust us, this one’s a must-have! 💎

The best part - it has no silver undertones or white pearly iridescence—instead, it reflects your natural undertone, delivering pure glitter that lets your skin shine. 🤍
